rows.label: xs02020150_MSG0001
rows.name:
Man, am I glad we pulled an assignment
to the east of the city this time.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs02020150_MSG0002
rows.name: It'd be a long walk all the way back over to the west gate.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs02020150_MSG0003
rows.name: Hold on...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs02020150_MSG0004
rows.name:
Are we even sure the east gate will be open? Last I heard,
it was still on lockdown from all the high-level indigen activity.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs02020150_MSG0005
rows.name:
It was, but they just lowered the threat level earlier today.
The gates are officially open for business.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs02020150_MSG0006
rows.name:
One of our teams must have gone out there
and kicked some furry indigen butt, huh?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs02020150_JNK0010
rows.name: Boast

rows.label: xs02020150_SEL0011
rows.name: Suggest it was you and Elma.

rows.label: xs02020150_JNK0020
rows.name: Speculate

rows.label: xs02020150_SEL0021
rows.name: Suggest it was Irina and Gwin.

rows.label: xs02020150_MSG0007
rows.name: Seriously? That was you? Cool![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs02020150_MSG0008
rows.name: I don't think so.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs02020150_MSG0009
rows.name:
Those grexes we took down were fairly routine—
definitely not something they'd lock both gates over, at least.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs02020150_MSG0010
rows.name: Then I take my "cool" back.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs02020150_MSG0011
rows.name: But wait a sec—you guys fought grexes? The two of you?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs02020150_MSG0012
rows.name: Hey, that's still pretty cool.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs02020150_MSG0013
rows.name:
They've been hassling a lot of teams lately,
especially how they hunt in packs and all.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs02020150_MSG0014
rows.name: Let's not get too excited.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs02020150_MSG0015
rows.name:
Confidence can be good.
Overconfidence can be fatal, especially when you're new.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs02020150_MSG0017
rows.name: Yeah, you're right.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs02020150_MSG0018
rows.name: Wouldn't surprise me at all. Irina's team is one of our best.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs02020150_MSG0020_m
rows.name: How does he know Irina and Gwin?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs02020150_MSG0020_f
rows.name: How does she know Irina and Gwin?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs02020150_MSG0021
rows.name:
We ran into them just before we met up with you.
They were on their way out to an assignment.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs02020150_MSG0022
rows.name: Well then that settles it! It must have been them, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs02020150_MSG0024
rows.name:
Maaaaaan, forget this amateur-hour probe baloney—
those guys are where the action's at.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs02020150_MSG0025
rows.name: I'll try not to take that personally.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs02020150_MSG0026
rows.name:
But enough talk—we've got our mission to deal with.
Let's head out.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs02020150_MSG0027
rows.name: Roger.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs02020150_MSG0028
rows.name:
That probe isn't gonna install itself.
Let's get to the east gate, shall we?[ST:wait ]
